	(layer "F.Cu")
	(descr "MP1584EN 5V fixed buck module, 22.3x17mm (portrait: 17mm wide, 22.3mm tall) per SZYTF datasheet. Surface-mount (reflow) — 8 castellated pads on the two short edges, 2 pads per corner group at 2.0mm pitch. Outer pad of each group bisected by the short edge (center at Y=±11.15); inner pad 2.0mm inboard (Y=±9.15). Pad column centers 1.5mm in from the long edges (X=±7.0, measured). IN+/IN- share one short end, OUT+/OUT- the other; IN+/OUT+ on left (-X), IN-/OUT- on right (+X).")
	(tags "buck converter MP1584EN 5V module direct mount SMD")
